  section.section-top-about#about
    .wrapper
      h2.sec-heading
        small Who We Are
        strong A HTML Coding Service<br> You Can Trust
      p.sec-description Choosing the right developer is a crucial decision that directly impacts your business, and we’re here to ensure you get the best results. Here’s what makes us stand out:
      ul.list-about
        li
          figure.item-image
            img(src=imgPC+"/about_img_01.jpg", width="504", height="350", loading="lazy", alt="No Upfront Payment – Pay Only When You're Satisfied")
          figure.item-content
            h3.item-title No Upfront Payment – Pay Only When You're Satisfied
            p.item-text We believe in delivering results before asking for payment. You’ll only pay after we provide a working demo and you are completely satisfied with the quality of our work.
        li
          figure.item-image
            img(src=imgPC+"/about_img_02.jpg", width="504", height="350", loading="lazy", alt="15+ Years of Experience")
          figure.item-content
            h3.item-title 15+ Years of Experience
            p.item-text With over 15 years of experience in Front-end Development, we understand exactly what clients need and ensure that our work meets all industry standards with precision and reliability
        li
          figure.item-image
            img(src=imgPC+"/about_img_03.jpg", width="504", height="350", loading="lazy", alt="Creator of the True Liquid Layout Method")
          figure.item-content
            h3.item-title Creator of the <a href="#" target="_blank">True Liquid Responsive</a> Method
            p.item-text True Liquid Responsive is an innovative responsive design method that perfectly scales across all screen sizes while preserving the original design proportions, including element sizes, spacing, typography, and line breaks.
        li
          figure.item-image
            img(src=imgPC+"/about_img_04.jpg", width="504", height="350", loading="lazy", alt="Consistent Coding Standards for High-Quality Work")
          figure.item-content
            h3.item-title Consistent Coding Standards for High-Quality Work
            p.item-text We follow our internal strict <a href="#" target="_blank">Coding Guidelines</a> to ensure clean, consistent, and maintainable code—no matter how many developers work on your project. Have your own standards? We’re happy to follow them too!
        li
          figure.item-image
            img(src=imgPC+"/about_img_05.jpg", width="504", height="350", loading="lazy", alt="Automated Code Quality Checks for Error-Free Results")
          figure.item-content
            h3.item-title Automated Code Quality Checks for Error-Free Results
            p.item-text We leverage task runners, pre-commit hooks, and automated code reviews to maintain high code quality. These automated processes help us catch issues early, ensuring that your project is always delivered with error-free, optimized, and well-structured code.
        li
          figure.item-image
            img(src=imgPC+"/about_img_06.jpg", width="504", height="350", loading="lazy", alt="Fast Turnaround &amp; On-Time Delivery")
          figure.item-content
            h3.item-title Fast Turnaround &amp; On-Time Delivery
            p.item-text We know deadlines matter. That’s why we deliver projects quickly while maintaining top-notch quality. Whether you need a standard or express delivery, we make sure you get reliable and professional results on time.

